# Observations recall: Typesense projection + sessions-search replacement

You are on flagg in `~/Code/joelhooks/joelclaw` (pnpm monorepo, Bun, Effect —
read `.claude/CLAUDE.md` and `AGENTS.md` first; validation checklist there is
mandatory). Governing decisions, read before coding:
`.brain/projects/wayfinder/build-observations-recall-typesense.svx` (your
ticket), `decide-observation-schema.svx` (Resolution — the file format),
`.brain/resources/decisions/files-are-truth-databases-are-projections.svx`.

## Build

1. **Collection**: `observations` in the Central Typesense (:8108, creds
   the CLI already uses). One doc per observation page in
   `~/Code/joelhooks/dark-wizard/.brain/observations/*.svx` (EXCLUDE the
   `proto-terra/` comparison subdir). Fields from schema-v1 frontmatter
   (sessionId, machine, agent, started, ended, tokens, repos[], privacy,
   slug) + parsed body: gist, observations[], decisions[], open_questions[],
   plus the canonical page URL
   (`https://brain.joelclaw.com/user/observations/<slug>/`).
2. **Indexer**: `joelclaw observations index [--rebuild]` — deterministic,
   idempotent projection from the files; `--rebuild` drops and re-creates
   the collection. Files are truth; the collection must be deletable and
   rebuilt byte-equivalent any time.
3. **Search replacement**: `joelclaw sessions search` defaults to the
   observation layer (query across gist/observations/decisions). Output per
   hit: gist snippet, sessionId, machine/agent/date, canonical page URL,
   and a clear `[sensitive]` label when `privacy: sensitive` (indexed for
   local recall by charter, but labeled so nothing gets shared onward
   thoughtlessly). Keep raw chunk search behind `--raw` (existing behavior,
   unchanged).
4. **Bug fix in the same code**: the sessions-search path defaults to
   ssh-host `dark-wizard` — a stale hostname from before this machine
   became flagg (it failed hard on 2026-07-12). Default to local when the
   machine is the current host; name the remote host correctly otherwise.

## Validate (per repo CLAUDE.md — all mandatory)

- `bunx tsc --noEmit` and `pnpm biome check packages/ apps/`
- `bun build packages/cli/src/cli.ts --compile --outfile ~/.bun/bin/joelclaw`
  then `joelclaw status` crash test
- Real receipts: `joelclaw observations index --rebuild` output;
  `joelclaw sessions search "observer topology"` returning the relevant
  observation page with its brain.joelclaw.com URL;
  `joelclaw sessions search --raw "observer topology"` still working.

## Rules

- Do NOT commit or push. Steering reviews and commits.
- No paid APIs; no new services; Typesense only (it's the chartered
  projection store).
- Effect v4 idioms per repo docs; imports across packages via `@joelclaw/*`.
- Print a DONE summary: files touched, collection stats (docs indexed),
  receipt outputs, anything ambiguous you decided.
